description:
CONNEXION
part of REISUB serie / CONNEXION
---------------------------------
>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>--- high res jpg 4000x4000
Probing a distant network, we receive an unknown signal, like nothing we've ever seen. 
A one-of-a-kind virus, that penetrated all of our defences.
Connexion is the first track of our album "REISUB" and tells the story 
of this first encounter. 
Check https://crashserver.fr for more info on our work
We livecode in front of an audience, and fight a never-dying server. 
There is so much more to come... stay tuned. 
Limited series, I will delete the source material once the mints
are gone. Be ready to crash. 
>> also check out nft collection @ https://hicetnunc.art/svdk_cs
>> and our procedural collection : https://www.fxhash.xyz/u/CrashServer
This collection is part of a larger project, stick around to see it emerge.
All links to our social networks are on our main website.
